dct_description_sm: Includes insets of "Budapest közlekedési Föútvonalai", [Budapest main traffic roads] and of "Római-part" indexed. Map shows city boundaries, districs are located by color coding, index tourist sites and important buildings. Panel title. Street index on verso. "1966-413/IV." City districts and major throughways are shown. Insets: Budapest kozlekedesi foutvanalai = [Budapest traffic thoroughfares], Romai-part = [Roman beach]. Index for bus and tram lines, points of interest on margin. Verso: Street index. Kartografiai Vallalt.
